                "text": " RoPE is not a positional embedding in the traditional sense — it is a transformation applied to query and key vectors inside each attention head. By making the attention score depend only on relative displacement m − n, it gives modern LLMs a principled notion of distance without any extra parameters, and enables practical context extension through base rescaling."
